{"tid":2080952,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"jerjer仔也能客製　《電馭叛客2077》自由度超高","createTime":"2020-06-26T22:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T17:56:55.000Z","uid":10063,"like":6,"dislike":126,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"3334ea1d3eb1859e84d6a603261470d50c102cce","tid":2080952,"uid":10063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T22:58:36.000Z","msg":"改大條Jer Jer仔同基努李維一同冒險 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />期待<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無興趣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/356/5e2130ed0b1ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F356%2F5e2130ed0b1ec.jpg&h=206e0574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCD Projekt RED的賽博龐克科幻大作《<span style=\"color: red;\">電馭叛客2077</span>》日前揭曉全新實機遊玩預告，帶來新的角色、故事及任務，並展示了Brain Dance編輯器，可以讓玩家體驗和分析遊戲中發生的一系列事件，在這個開放世界遊戲體驗與故事情節中扮演重要角色，本作中，玩家將扮演義體改造的傭兵「V」，並與<span style=\"color: red;\">基努李維</span>飾演的Jonny Silverhand一同冒險。<br />\n<br />\n在《電馭叛客2077》裡，角色自定義的選項非常豐富，外媒Kotaku透露，其中含有6種膚色、35種髮型、17雙眼睛、5種牙齒、8種眼妝、8種眉型、17種下巴、17雙耳朵、8個賽博龐克組件、9種疤痕、6種紋身，玩家甚至能<span style=\"color: red;\">調整胸部及那話兒的尺寸</span>，高自由度的客製化令人嘆為觀止。<br />\n <br />\n（已節錄）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/gadget/20200627/X4A5YCWXEE7J6QYMOLRVI2NG4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fgadget%2F20200627%2FX4A5YCWXEE7J6QYMOLRVI2NG4M%2F&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=579d7a74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fgadget%2F20200627%2FX4A5YCWXEE7J6QYMOLRVI2NG4M%2F&h=ba70b68a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/gadget/20200627/X4A5YCWXEE7J6QYMOLRVI2NG4M/</a><br />\n<br />\n_______